Interface RdaCloudletScheduler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RdaCloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload

    public interface RdaCloudletScheduler
    This interface enhanced the VM scheduler with the necessary methods that are required to be implemented when using the RDA module.
    Author:
    Patrick A. Taddei

      • updateVmProcessing

        double updateVmProcessing(double currentTime,
                        List<Double> mipsShare,
                        double bwShare,
                        double storageIOShare)
        Updates the processing of cloudlets running under management of this scheduler.
        Parameters:
        currentTime - current simulation time
        mipsShare - list with MIPS share of each Pe available to the scheduler
        bwShare - bandwidth share available
        storageIOShare - storage IO share available
        Returns:
        time predicted completion time of the earliest finishing cloudlet
